content:
This build was released on the 4th of February, 2024.
This is the official release of version 1.0.
There are 450 total stars, including 13 newly added Green Stars.
This version introduced 52 new areas which you can see here:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1HhX6ldAGSTQxWO--DQ28KYCAQeOZw8FzfvuUC8fUG6g/view?gid=149881732
